md-content.md-whiteframe-z1(ng-if="!$ctrl._authenticationService.isAuthenticated()" layout-padding)
  h3 Connexion
  form(name="connectForm")
    div(layout="row" layout-xs="column")
      md-input-container
        label Login
        input(type="text" required ng-model="credentials.username")
      md-input-container
        label Mot de passe
        input(type="password" required ng-model="credentials.password")
    .md-actions(layout="row" layout-align="space-around")
      md-button.md-primary.md-raised(
        ng-click="$ctrl._authenticationService.connect(credentials)"
        ng-disabled="!connectForm.$valid"
      ) Se connecter
  div(layout="row" layout-align="center")
    a(ng-link="['LoginCreate']" href="#") Pas enregistré? Je crée un compte !

md-content.md-whiteframe-z1(ng-if="$ctrl._authenticationService.isAuthenticated()" layout-padding)
  | Vous êtes déjà connecté en tant que
  span.bold {{$ctrl._authenticationService.user.username}}
  .md-actions(layout="row" layout-align="space-around")
    md-button.md-primary.md-raised(ng-click="$ctrl._authenticationService.disconnect()") Se déconnecter



